    <briefdescription>
<para>Mega-fused attention decode with Q5_0 weights - Header. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This header declares the mega-fused attention decode kernel that combines 9 separate operations into a single fused kernel call:<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>RMSNorm</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Q projection (Q5_0) with bias</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>K projection (Q5_0) with bias</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>V projection (Q8_0) with bias</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>RoPE application</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>KV cache store</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Flash attention decode (GQA-aware)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>O projection (Q5_0) with bias</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Residual add </para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
